{"tid":1678280,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"RTHK攝影師旺角採訪期間遭防暴警推撞及強行扯脫面罩 有警員向一名外籍人士問「你CIA呀? 」","createTime":"2019-10-27T14:49:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T14:34:59.000Z","uid":212626,"like":113,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"9da9fe783495d638e06f59832f48004b1ff08e03","tid":1678280,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T14:49:29.000Z","msg":"本台攝影師晚上在旺角彌敦道採訪期間，被防暴警察阻撓及推撞，並強行脫下面罩，警方在現場曾多次施放催淚彈。<span style=\"color: red;\">本台攝影師當時戴著記者證，並身穿印有港台標誌的反光衣，攝影機亦貼上港台標誌</span>。<br />\n<br />\n本台攝影師當時在行人路上拍攝，一名持長槍的防暴警員突然走向他，推他的肩膀，強行扯下他的面罩，又推開攝影機。<br />\n<br />\n十多名防暴警員到場分隔開該名警員及圍觀人士，又手持盾牌及警棍，要求在場其他記者及市民走開。<span style=\"color: red;\">有警員向一名外籍人士問「你CIA呀? 」</span>，外籍人士之後離開。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488492-20191027.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488492-20191027.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4TsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=efcd2edc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488492-20191027.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=86bd77c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488492-20191027.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"bbe0687e3174600b77b4935e58d265ea65acb97c","tid":1678280,"uid":195252,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T14:50:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都係FIB呀"},{"pid":"ee9aeb8d4c478db7e1b24ac981780ab3388dee29","tid":1678280,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T14:50:27.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，推post &amp; 借個 靚位<br />\n鐘庭耀為今次運動發起全港性民調，追蹤長期民意<br />\n<br />\n連登post: 鍾庭耀教授都企左出來....你仲做冷氣軍師??<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n眾籌link: <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\